 "description": "A structured evidence matrix comparing RegDEEP™ NISM Mock test Series 2026 & conventional / traditional exam prep materials available across public domain. Most mock test series focus only on question practice. RegDEEP™ is designed as a regulatory decoding framework aligned with examiner intent, regulatory interpretation, and decision logic used in NISM certification examinations. This Dataset table highlights 23 specific ways in which the RegDEEP™ framework differs from conventional mock test series used for NISM exam preparation.",
"disambiguatingDescription": "This dataset represents an independent, research-based, illustrative comparison table created for educational and exam-preparation purposes. It is compiled using publicly available information, officially published syllabus details, and test objective contexts applicable from January 2026 onward for different NISM exams. This comparison analyzes the NISM Exam module's examination framework in relation to the RegDEEP™ Series 2026 and typical mock test or exam prep materials offerings available in the market. This is NOT an official NISM publication, document, endorsement, or certified data source. It does not represent, reproduce, or replace any official NISM material. Learners are advised to refer to the official NISM website and prescribed workbook for authoritative information regarding examination structure, fees, syllabus, and regulatory updates.",
